data.description:
A beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath located within a gated community and on a cul-de-sac! This gated community also features a pool for residents! Walking in you'll find a spacious foyer leading into the open concept living/kitchen area. Not only a great space for entertaining, but the kitchen has plenty of storage. Downstairs you'll also find a half bath, garage access and the fenced backyard. Upstairs there is a great flex space perfect for home office, reading nook or guest space. The master bedroom has a large bathroom attached with double vanity and tiled shower. Two additional bedrooms are spacious with plenty of closet space. A well maintained home, close to bases, shopping, school and the beaches. Give us a call to schedule a showing! Pets Accepted upon Owner Approval

Smoking allowed:No
